name: [LoRa] Gem & Gear/宝石と歯車 Concept
description:
This is a model that generates gems and jewelry which trained by 150 img.

When weight 0.7~0.8 you can use gem as ornaments for figures or animals, and weight 1.0 maybe generates just gems and jewelry .

Recommend prompts such as gem,gear,jewelry,no human and so on

It's a experimental work, have fun （：3っ）∋
